# Introduction

This repository ports the C++ decoder code from [Kaldi][Kaldi]
using [OpenFst][OpenFst] without depending on [Kaldi][Kaldi].

[Kaldi]: https://github.com/kaldi-asr/kaldi
[OpenFst]: https://www.openfst.org/


